Package com.example.geoquizfrontend.services

Interface ApiService

public interface ApiService
ApiService is a Retrofit interface that defines the endpoints for the GeoQuiz API. It provides methods for sending HTTP requests and receiving HTTP responses from the server. The methods are annotated with HTTP request types (GET, POST, PUT) and the corresponding endpoint URLs.
